# Docker instructions

Start a docker data volume by

    docker run -v /data -name DATA tianon/true

Start the docker container for sidekiq workers

    docker run --volumes-from DATA bibstha/bharkhar-workers

Start docker container for web server. This runs a rails app in production mode. `bibstha/bharkhar-server` exposes port 3000, we map it to host port 3000. Make sure to host nginx by proxing 

    docker run --volumes-from DATA -p 3000:3000 bibstha/bharkhar-server

